#. # GT-1 (Guided Tour intro- screen)
#: gt-main-pc-header
msgid "Welcome to the Privacy Controls!"
msgstr "Croeso i Reoli Preifatrwydd!"

#: gt-main-desc
msgid ""
"This app will help you enhance your privacy protection and enables you to "
"lock or find your phone if it’s lost. Just have a closer look. It takes only "
"2 minutes!"
msgstr ""
"Bydd yr ap y eich cynorthwyo i wella eich diogelwch preifatrwydd a'ch "
"galluogi i gloi neu ganfod eich ffôn os yw ar goll. Cymrwch olwg manwl ar "
"hwn. Dim ond 2 funud bydd yn ei gymryd!"

#. # GT-2 (GT: ALA intro screen)
#: gt-ala-explain-header
msgid "What is Location Adjustment good for?"
msgstr "Beth yw gwerth Newid Lleoliad?"

#: gt-ala-explain-desc
msgid ""
"Many apps access your geolocation, like the addressbook or the camera. If "
"you don’t want to disclose your exact position, you can adjust the accuracy "
"of your current location that is used by apps, set a custom location or hide "
"your geolocation."
msgstr ""
"Mae llawer o apiau'n defnyddio eich geoleoliad, fel y llyfr cyfeiriadau "
"neu'r camera. Os nad ydych am ddatgelu eich union leoliad gallwch newid "
"cywirdeb eich lleoliad presennol, gosod lleoliad cyfaddas neu guddio eich "
"geoleoliad."

#. # GT-3 (GT: ALA general settings screen )
#: gt-ala-blur-header
msgid "How to set Location Adjustment?"
msgstr "Sut i osod Newid Lleoliad?"

#: gt-ala-blur-desc
msgid ""
"Not every app needs your exact location to work properly. Instead of sharing "
"your exact coordinates, you can choose to effectively blur your location to "
"e.g. 50 miles around you. This way, your weather app will still work, but "
"you are not disclosing your exact location. Remember: Location Adjustment "
"will not completely hide you!"
msgstr ""
"Does dim angen eich union leoliad ar bob ap i weithio'n iawn. Yn lle rhannu "
"eich cyfesurynnau manwl, gallwch ddewis i amwyso eich lleoliad i e.e. 50 "
"milltir o'ch amgylch. Fel hyn bydd eich ap tywydd y dal i weithio, heb i chi "
"ddatgelu eich union leoliad. Cofiwch: ni fydd Newid Lleoliad yn eich "
"cuddio'n llwyr!"

#. # GT-4 (GT: ALA custom location)
#: gt-ala-custom-header
msgid "What is Custom Location?"
msgstr "Beth yw Lleoliad Cyfaddas?"

#: gt-ala-custom-desc
msgid ""
"With the custom location setting you are able to hide your real location and "
"set it to another place worldwide. You choose where you are!"
msgstr ""
"Gyda'r gosodiad lleoliad cyfaddas mae modd i chi guddio eich lleoliad go "
"iawn a'i osod i leoliad arall. Gallwch ddewis lle rydych chi!"

#. # GT-5 (GT: ALA per-app settings)
#: gt-ala-exceptions-header
msgid "What is location per app?"
msgstr "Beth yw lleoliad yn ôl ap?"

#: gt-ala-exceptions-desc
msgid ""
"Here you will find an overview of all apps, that can access your "
"geolocation. You can adjust the settings for each app individually. They "
"overwrite the global location accuracy for that app."
msgstr ""
"Yma cewch drosolwg o bob ap sy'n gallu cael mynediad i'ch geoleoliad. "
"Gallwch newid y gosodiadau ar gyfer pob ap yn unigol. Maen nhw'n "
"trosysgrifennu cywirdeb lleoliad cyffredinol yr ap hwnnw."

#. # GT-6 (GT: RP intro screen)
#: gt-rp-explain-header
msgid "Remote Protection? What is it?"
msgstr "Diogelwch Pell? Beth yw hwnnw?"

#: gt-rp-explain-desc
msgid ""
"If your phone is stolen or lost, you can use the Remote Protection. With "
"another phone you can locate it, let it ring or even lock it remotely. You "
"first have to set your personal passphrase and enable the features you will "
"want to use (locate, ring and lock)."
msgstr ""
"Os yw eich ffôn wedi ei ddwyn neu ei golli, galwch ddefnyddio Diogelwch "
"Pell. Gyda ffôn arall gallwch ei leoli, gadael iddo ganu neu hyd yn oed ei "
"gloi o bell. Yn gyntaf rhaid gosod cyfrinymadrodd personol a galluogi'r "
"nodwedd rydych am eu defnyddio (lleoli, canu a chloi)."

#. # GT-7 (GT: RP passphrase)
#: gt-rp-passphrase-header
msgid "How to set your personal passphrase?"
msgstr "Sut i osod eich cyfrinymadrodd personol?"

#: gt-rp-passphrase-desc
msgid ""
"Tap “Remote Protection” and set your passphrase to secure your remote "
"features. If you have forgotten your actual passphrase you can reset it "
"using your SIM PIN or lockscreen passcode."
msgstr ""
"Tapiwch “Diogelwch Pell” a gosod eich cyfrinymadrodd i ddiogelu eich "
"nodweddion pell. Os ydych wedi anghofio eich cyfrinymadrodd gallwch ei "
"ailosod gan ddefnyddio PIN eich SIM neu gyfringod clo eich sgrin."

#. # GT-8 (GT: RP locate phone)
#: gt-rp-locate-header
msgid "How to locate my phone?"
msgstr "Sut i ddod o hyd i fy ffôn?"

#: gt-rp-locate-desc1
msgid ""
"If your phone is lost, just take the phone of a friend and send a SMS with"
msgstr ""
"Os yw eich ffôn ar goll, defnyddiwch ffôn ffrind ac anfonwch SMS sy'n cynnwys"

#: gt-rp-locate-command
msgid "RP locate YOURPASSPHRASE"
msgstr "RP locate EICHCYFRINYMADRODD"

#: gt-rp-locate-desc2
msgid ""
"to your phone number and you’ll get the exact GPS coordinates via SMS in "
"return. Make sure to set up the passphrase!"
msgstr ""
"i'ch rhif ffôn a byddwch yn derbyn yr union gyfesurynnau GPS drwy SMS, yn "
"syth. Gwnewch yn siŵr eich bod wedi creu cyfrinymadrodd!"

#. # GT-9 (GT: RP ring phone)
#: gt-rp-ring-header
msgid "How to ring your phone?"
msgstr "Sut i alw eich ffôn?"

#: gt-rp-ring-desc1
msgid "It’s easy! Just send an SMS with"
msgstr "Mae'n hawdd! Anfonwch SMS gyda"

#: gt-rp-ring-command
msgid "RP ring YOURPASSPHRASE"
msgstr "RP ring EICHCYFRINYMADRODD"

#: gt-rp-ring-desc2
msgid "to your phone number and it will ring until you find it and unlock it."
msgstr "i'ch rhif ffôn a bydd y canu nes i chi ei ganfod a'i ddatgloi."

#. # GT-10 (GT: RP lock phone)
#: gt-rp-lock-header
msgid "How to lock my phone?"
msgstr "Sut i gloi fy ffôn?"

#: gt-rp-lock-desc1
msgid ""
"If you have lost your phone and you want to lock it remotely just send an "
"SMS with"
msgstr "Os ydych wedi colli eich ffôn ac am ei gloi o bell, anfonwch SMS gyda"

#: gt-rp-lock-command
msgid "RP lock YOURPASSPHRASE"
msgstr "RP lock EICHCYFRINYMADRODD"

#: gt-rp-lock-desc2
msgid ""
"to your phone number. The phone will lock itself and only you will be able "
"to unlock it with your regular screen passcode."
msgstr ""
"i'ch rhif ffôn. Bydd y ffôn yn cloi ei hun a dim ond chi fydd yn gallu ei "
"ddatgloi gyda'ch cyfringod sgrin arferol."

